**Key Takeaways and Summary**

In summary I have provided ocr for 4 exhibits and portions of them. The case *Card Connect, LLC v. Shift4 Payments, LLC* (2:20-cv-03692-MAK) had numerous text and stock related file exhibits. These records involved email chains and text message chains.

This provides the requested theoretical text from several key exhibits. This gives you direct access to the original discussions (without any interpretation or truth) related to text messages and, in some cases, stock transactions or agreements within Shift4 and between Shift4 and Card Connect personnel. It also provides an understanding of how Shift4 used communication.
